{"tid":155446,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 點樣先可以擺脫負面情緒?","createTime":"2017-03-14T04:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T17:11:09.000Z","uid":45627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a662aef96e65e91b091785039c0c837355d255a4","tid":155446,"uid":45627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:54:27.000Z","msg":"自問未嚴重到有抑鬱<br />\n但偏偏就係提唔起勁, 諗嘢好負面<br />\n每日都咁其實好辛苦<br />\n同時又影響到另一半同朋友<br />\n試問有邊個鐘意身邊嘅人日日都散發負能量?<br />\n<br />\n有時半夜靜靜地問自己<br />\n到底係為乜野唔開心, 為乜日日喊<br />\n但就係搵唔到答案, 明明又冇咩大事發生<br />\n慢慢覺得係一種病態<br />\n<br />\n到底要點做先可以擺脫依家呢種情緒?<br />\n我都好想每日輕輕鬆鬆, 開開心心咁過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8eeec64a27de3de98143da9de580e12aa3b91c4","tid":155446,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:57:44.000Z","msg":"低落情緒維持幾耐?<br />\n如果長時間我覺得要睇下醫生"},{"pid":"b244b812d05020bd78122efc95a79dc9f6ef6b89","tid":155446,"uid":85929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:02:37.000Z","msg":"幾時開始係咁<br />\n嗰陣有冇發生過啲咩事"},{"pid":"ee14eea868e7cbcfc559f7bb7be835b2d658baf7","tid":155446,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:07:36.000Z","msg":"開心又係咁過<br />\n唔開心又係咁過<br />\n<br />\n點解要開心咁過？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實黎留名<br />\n我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca1d6f95b06038ec4934f300bf37593a7534f96","tid":155446,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:11:33.000Z","msg":"控制唔到情緒應該睇醫生"},{"pid":"50174f5588388f3f3eead2831ae9bf13ddde30dc","tid":155446,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:12:11.000Z","msg":"同埋呢個世界冇人可以完全正面<br />\n你要學點樣同負面共存"},{"pid":"6c06781225bba450e2f1b38a31dd01de5896b689","tid":155446,"uid":21664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20